aptana studio ( web app IDE)

Creating web sites and applications on your platform 
of choice is now easier than ever. Aptana's PHP, Ruby 
on Rails and Jaxer application engines come ready to 
use and ready to scale in Aptana Studio, Eclipse and 
Aptana Cloud. Develop against local or remote engines. 
Deploy and scale on demand. 

Homepage, http://www.aptana.com/studio

DEPENDENCIES:
  * xulrunner
